data.description: Explore this Ranch-Style Home, boasting 3 Bedrooms and 2 Bathrooms, located on a spacious one-acre plot near Lake Lanier. This property is free from HOA restrictions, offering ample storage space for boats and RVs. It features a heated 2-car garage and interiors with hardwood and tile flooring. The kitchen has granite countertops and new cabinets on the lower level. The master bedroom includes a large deck, and the en-suite bathroom has a walk-in shower and closet. Key updates include a relatively new roof and HVAC system. ThereCOs also a sizable laundry room and abundant parking space. Plenty of room for your RV and Boat. The property also features a newer 24x32 shed in the backyard and a large 14x28 deck, ready for entertaining with multi-levels and a Koi pond.
